            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Crush your <strong>cashew</strong> <strong>nuts</strong> in their bag with a <strong>rolling</strong> <strong>pin</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don’t have a rolling pin, just chop them roughly!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688483155510-x200.jpg",
