            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>,<strong> umami seasoning</strong>,<strong> </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>cornflour</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[6 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp]</span> <strong>water </strong>and stir it all together<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
