            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Combine the <strong>crushed cashews </strong>in a separate bowl with the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>spicy cashew crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688483163271-x200.jpg",
