          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>hoisin & pepper noodle stir-fry </strong>in a bowl and garnish with the <strong>spicy cashew crumb</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the spicy cashew crumb!</span></strong></p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> if needed</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
